locality: Madagascar. Prov. Fianarantsoa. Andringitra mountains S of Fianarantsoa. NW facing mountain slopes in the northern part of the National Park. Forest with low trees. Epiphytic on Vaccinium (Anderberg et al. 44). Flowers yellow and red.
Madagascar. Prov. Antananarivo. Special Reserve of Ambohitantely. Rainforest. Epiphytic on Vaccinium. Flowers red at base and yellow at tip.
